Experiments with Solidity and Ethereum
===

This repository consists of code used to create and test solidity contracts. 

Pre-requistises used:
- nodejs 4.x
- truffle framework
- ubuntu 16.04
- testrpc (for testing solidity contracts)
- ethereumjs

Based on the tutorial provided by BitCorp's Manuel Araoz
https://medium.com/bitcorps-blog/the-hitchhikers-guide-to-smart-contracts-in-ethereum-848f08001f05#.2hurzng0w

-
